abstract = {This entry reviews the definition of trolling as well as the qualities of trolls and the targets of trolling. Various definitions of online trolling are presented to reflect the range of disciplines that have attended to the scholarship of trolling. Online trolling is contrasted with cyberbullying. The significance of anonymity and humor to trolling are emphasized as the distinguishing qualities. The range of motives for trolls, including humor, deception, and disruption are reviewed. The demographic and psychosocial profiles of both perpetrators and targets of trolling are presented.}
